description: Explore the enigmatic world of dreams and discover all their meanings. Through vivid examples and practical tips, explore how dreams can provide clues to our emotions, desires and unresolved challenges. From interpreting symbols to analyzing recurring patterns, this game will help you decipher the language of dreams and use that wisdom to improve your daily life and explore their entire universe in a fascinating and enriching way.
name: The Meaning of Dreams
intro: Discover The Meaning of Dreams and reveal your emotions and desires! It will help you decipher their symbology and use that wisdom in your daily life.
